# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge

We as members, contributors, and leaders pledge to make participation in our project a harassment-free experience for everyone.

## Our Standards

Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment:
- Respectful and inclusive language
- Graceful acceptance of constructive criticism
- Focus on what is best for the community

Examples of unacceptable behavior:
- Trolling or insulting remarks
- Personal or political attacks
- Public or private harassment

## Enforcement

Instances of abusive behavior may be reported by contacting the project maintainer at [your email].

Maintainers have the right to remove, edit, or reject comments and contributions that do not align with this Code of Conduct.
